``` sql
SELECT * FROM performance_schema.host_cache
WHERE COUNT_CONNECT_ERRORS > 0
   OR COUNT_HANDSHAKE_ERRORS > 0
   OR COUNT_AUTHENTICATION_ERRORS > 0
   OR COUNT_MAX_USER_CONNECTIONS_ERRORS > 0
ORDER BY COUNT_CONNECT_ERRORS DESC
LIMIT 20;
```

also [[Check Blocked Hosts in Mysql NDB]] if you're using ndb
